            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p>Heliophilia Eyewear</p>
            
            <p>Heliophilia is a high-end sunglasses brand that captures the marriage of beauty and functionality in our classic but edgy designs. Heliophilia products elevate simplicity with unique shapes and creative usage of materials.</p><!--Short description of the company-->
            
            <h2>Target audience</h2>
            
            <p>Our company will target the young adult to middle-aged adult demographic, ages ranging from 19 to 60 years, and those of all genders. We expect our consumer base to have a fairly affluent lifestyle and/or values quality purchases.</p><!-- Who are the people who use this site? -->
           
            <p>Users of this site will be searching/shopping for a pair of sunglasses that firstly, have premium-quality UV resistance, but secondly, make a refreshing style statement while achieving their minimalist style prefences. </p><!-- What are their primary task and goals? -->
            
           
